      "description": "This car is in good condition. It runs and drives well with no significant mechanical issues. The exterior shows minor surface imperfections consistent with normal use, but no major scratches or dents. The interior has light wear on high-contact areas but is otherwise clean and functional. A solid, reliable vehicle.",
